creator: NDW Enterprises
descriptionHtml:
Eclipse is a safe, guided space to interact with the innermost parts of you to create authentic healing through meditations call TERMs - Transformational Emotional Release Meditations. These guided meditations will support your desire to heal through the natural phases and rhythms of life. While using the Eclipse App, you will see meditations are organized by icons indicating a moon phase. Starting with new moon and crescent, followed by full moon, and culminating in Eclipse, each phase will take you deeper and closer to your goals.

You will find the Eclipse App interface is simple to use. Download to access our growing library of soundscape meditations. Here you can browse by topics such as anxiety, weight loss, creativity and more, to find meditations, clearings, and affirmation tracks to support you. This expansive library of resources allows you to find peace you need at any moment. You may find yourself playing affirmations in the background of your busy morning, pausing for 5 minutes of meditation before your next task, or planning time to complete a full TERM to assist with deep healing.
